sentences: Lars Gunnar Wiklund (17 August 1935 – 29 September 1989) was a Swedish singer.
He scored several Svensktoppen hits, and participated in Melodifestivalen four times.
Lars Gunnar Wiklund was born on 17 August 1935 in Luleå, Sweden, as the first child of Ellen and Sven Wiklund.
